column1: POPULATION BY DISTRICTS, AGE AND SEX AS OF 31.12.*

Note: The revision is done in accordence to Eurostat general strategy on recalculation of the population number between censuses. Data are recalculated based on the 2011 and 2021 census results, as well as on data on natural and migration increase during the respective period.
*Post-census revision of population by districts, sex and age has been recalculated as of 2.12.2024
